rows.label: qst200505_msg001
rows.name:
You want to know where
Alban-san's ship ran aground?

rows.label: qst200505_msg002
rows.name: I was a fledgling navigator back then.

rows.label: qst200505_msg003
rows.name:
Well, it was my first voyage. Between
the nervousness and the violent rocking
of the ship, I got seasick.

rows.label: qst200505_msg004
rows.name:
My mind was hazy... I
barely remember anything.

rows.label: qst200505_msg005
rows.name:
But, I'm sure it was facing the
Cloud Sea. Because I went outside
and threw up right away...
